title: # 21 – Something’s Burning Uncut – Eleanor Kerrigan & Rick Ingraham
description:
Something’s Burning Uncut is the uncut audio from my cooking show “Something’s Burning” on YouTube.

On this episode that originally aired on YouTube May 27, 2019 Eleanor Kerrigan and Rick Ingraham (The Comedy Store Podcast) learn how to make Deep-fried Mac and Cheese Balls and Waffle Iron Corn Dogs.
